# Gemini API Key for AI Search Audit
# 1. Get your API Key from Google AI Studio: https://aistudio.google.com/
# 2. For LOCAL development: Create a file named '.env' and add the line below.
# 3. For VERCEL deployment: Add this variable in Vercel Dashboard > Settings > Environment Variables.
# IMPORTANT: The 'VITE_' prefix is REQUIRED for the variable to be accessible in the browser.

VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
